                    "body": "Extracted from a proof below:\r\n```suggestion\r\n\r\nlemma fundamentalDomain_pi_basisFun [Fintype ι] [DecidableEq ι] :\r\n    fundamentalDomain (Pi.basisFun ℝ ι) = Set.pi Set.univ fun _ : ι ↦ Set.Ico (0 : ℝ) 1 := by\r\n  ext; simp\r\n\r\n```",
